description: A few broken paving stones have survived from the badly weathered road.  Most of the pavers have sunk below the surface of the surrounding grass.  To the south, the road improves somewhat.

A few broken paving stones have survived from the badly weathered road, creating a stumbling hazard in the nighttime darkness.  Most of the pavers have sunk below the surface of the surrounding grass.  To the south, the road improves somewhat.
title: [Gyldemar Forest, Ancient Road]
